parameters:
Anomalocaris: Moss moss... The hidden camera I set up in the
shower room doesn't seem to have been found at all! Looks
like I can peep as much as I want for a while!

Henchman: All members of the organization are glued to the
live video URL!! Hehehe, that girl lives here, so she takes
showers morning and night... and we get to see every single
moment of it.

Underling: Grr... As former subordinates of the great Shark
Broccoli boss, we'd like to report this to Lord Shark
Duke... but we've been silenced by the new boss... and
saying it now might just shock him...

Memimi has fallen into Anomalocaris's trap, and her daily
bathing scenes are being spied on by all members of the same
organization...!

Anomalocaris: ...By the way, I've beaten that little girl
twice and made her my subordinate... Someone as great as me
shouldn't need to sneak around the shower room, maybe she'd
even accept bathing together...

Anomalocaris: Honestly, lately when she looks at me, I feel
something beyond anger or hatred... Through our battles,
we've connected hearts and bonded deeply, something only we
can understand... Maybe this is... doable...!!

Anomalocaris: Cut the hidden camera feed!! From now on, I
will personally show her mercy!! I'll make her fall head
over heels for me physically and turn her into my lover~!!
